jobs.jobDescription:
• Developed and expanded automated testing using Selenium and integrated them into Jenkins.
  • Wrote Python code to improve software projects and addressed security vulnerabilities.
  • Led the integration of software projects, including setup of MATLAB and Python environments.
  • Participated in software development projects to meet Air Force customer requirements.

• Key developer for front-end and back-end support in various software projects.
  • Developed applications with Oracle SQL, improving data management and user interfaces.
  • Initiated builds for Python-based projects, contributing to the company's development process.
  • Improved user interfaces for better client feedback and project lead approval.

• Designed and programmed automated regression tests for applications.
  • Updated older tests to work with new software testing tools.

• Integrated new monitoring functionality for customer data analysis.
  • Developed a Java server/client application for data management and storage in ElasticSearch.
  • Created a JavaScript web interface using Google Maps API to display data from ElasticSearch.
• Designed a desktop application in VB.NET / Visual C# for chiropractic business management, enabling paperless record keeping.
